{"tid":1024991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國玻璃心】ZARA廣告被指辱華 因中國模特兒滿臉雀斑？","createTime":"2019-02-17T04:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T08:08:44.000Z","uid":13468,"like":6,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3c799be8e126ec2e62efb684f51b3359409483d3","tid":1024991,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:08:16.000Z","msg":"【強國玻璃心】ZARA廣告被指辱華 因中國模特兒滿臉雀斑？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190217/large/1550368781_0b85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190217%2Flarge%2F1550368781_0b85.jpg&h=ed8ccff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼意大利奢侈品牌DG廣告被指辱華後，西班牙服裝品牌ZARA近日也陷入爭議。ZARA上周五在微博發佈最新彩妝產品宣傳廣告，當中中國模特兒李靜雯滿臉雀斑的照片，引發內地網民爭論，指ZARA的安排是刻意醜化亞洲女性，更有網民直指ZARA辱華。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於廣告宣傳照上的李靜雯滿臉雀斑，網民看法可謂兩極，有部份網民認為照片「好看、真實」，並稱「這是自信美」，指大部份人都習慣活在「美顏中」。但亦有不少網民「玻璃心」，直指照片「毫無美感」、「譁眾取寵」，「是在醜化亞洲人嗎？ 」更指看罷ZARA廣告後，影響購買慾云云。<br />\n對此，ZARA回應稱沒有刻意醜化亞洲女性，稱ZARA的宣傳是面向全球，不是針對中國市場，而且模特是由西班牙總部選出，照片是在自然狀態下完成拍攝，只是與內地人審美觀不同而已。<br />\n資料顯示，廣告中的中國模特兒李靜雯，16歲時進入模特兒行業。有網民稱，李靜雯特點之一就是她的小雀斑，並指另一較知名的中國模特兒呂燕，也是典型的東方臉和有雀斑。<br />\n意大利奢侈品牌DG早前曾陷入辱華風波，去年11月，DG推出引起爭議的「起筷吃飯」廣告，設計師隨後更辱罵「中國是屎國」，觸發不少「愛國」明星出面抵制，最終DG兩名創辦人兼設計師一同拍片道歉。<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190217/59268999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F59268999&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=c68ccba6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F59268999&h=e5febb3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190217/59268999</a>"},{"pid":"145cfc9b0fb754b77e1b512e66b141367938a931","tid":1024991,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:10:06.000Z","msg":"罷買Zara <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 改用淘寶買衫算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4670d5193827b9052d52c9b6b103abafb72b8eca","tid":1024991,"uid":24345,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"條女做到model已經好俾面支那"},{"pid":"39333589156e5bbda464368820c19a372918a36c","tid":1024991,"uid":17641,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"下次搵隻支那肥雞著到好似楊貴妃咁好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd7a788b04d334a71e05f958bef89649c078ef9","tid":1024991,"uid":211461,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"辱華已成萬能key<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5c286d443b9dd77054366159a810ca2be53e12","tid":1024991,"uid":2054,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"So辱華！"},{"pid":"74ad8bad1cecf7f936b158a1f7c7a2d74a205b4a","tid":1024991,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"係啊係啊  你覺得係辱華就辱華啦支拿仔<br />\n買洶寶cancer衫著囉笨柒"},{"pid":"1c42424fcf63420946f5ed89c371536558a9ccc7","tid":1024991,"uid":74442,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"辱華低能都唔講，重要見識少<br />\n啲大陸閪 google 下 lululemon model trypophobia 咩先叫核突啦"},{"pid":"b7c351c7c866a890c798d0eee1c4138f837447ab","tid":1024991,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"辱華辱華辱華   華你老味咩  辱支咋"},{"pid":"9afb3ce93be777a002089dd07c38c0893b17975b","tid":1024991,"uid":44690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c42424fcf63420946f5ed89c371536558a9ccc7","tid":1024991,"uid":74442,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:20:39.000Z","msg":"辱華低能都唔講，重要見識少<br />\n啲大陸閪 google 下 lululemon model trypophobia 咩先叫核突啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T04:2